						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://extropolitica.wordpress.com/2013/04/06/bitcoin-lintroduzione-libertaria/" rel="bookmark">Bitcoin &#8211; L&#8217;introduzione Libertaria</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://extropolitica.wordpress.com/2013/04/06/bitcoin-lintroduzione-libertaria/" title="3:36 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-04-06T15:36:00+00:00">aprile 6, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://extropolitica.wordpress.com/author/painlord2k/" title="Vedi tutti gli articoli di painlord2k" rel="author">painlord2k</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
